item.title: Schokolade
item.description: Nic and I went to Windsor on Sunday on a whim. I took Nic to Carluccio’s for the first time. She was very pleased with the ciocolatte Fiorentina - it’s nice that little things make her so happy. :-) We also wandered round the castle for a bit and took at quick trip to the shops to buy my mums birthday present.
